metadata.description: As you scroll through the collection, you can't help but be mesmerized by the pixelated octopuses that swim across your screen. Each one is unique, with its own personality and charm. Some are mischievous, while others are more reserved. But they all have one thing in common: they are all made up of tiny pixels, each one carefully placed to create these digital sea creatures.
metadata.name: NotSoScaryOctopus #1
